I was young and ignorant back then.

344
00:18:39,700 --> 00:18:40,740
I'm different now.

345
00:18:41,160 --> 00:18:42,080
Let me try again.

346
00:18:45,010 --> 00:18:46,500
What's that magic?

347
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:09,560
Don't waste time.

348
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:16,820
Lan.

349
00:19:16,970 --> 00:19:19,000
