393
00:22:19,440 --> 00:22:20,210
Take a guess.

394
00:22:50,690 --> 00:22:51,500
Father.

395
00:22:51,620 --> 00:22:52,340
Don't be afraid.

396
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:54,150
I don't want to hurt you.

397
00:22:54,240 --> 00:22:55,350
As long as you promise me

398
00:22:55,450 --> 00:22:56,660
